2 To apply the Promiſes orderly, is to apply the promiſes of grace, before the promiſes of glory. Men are not to look upon the promiſes of ſalvation, before they look upon the promiſes of Juſtification, adoption, and Sanctification: For God ſaves none, nor will ſave none, but thoſe that are firſt juſtified, ſanctified, and adopted;
